## Daily Exercise 17
url = '~/github/geog-13-labs/data/uscities.csv'
uscities <- read_csv(url)
## 
##  Column specification 
## cols(
##   city = col_character(),
##   city_ascii = col_character(),
##   state_id = col_character(),
##   state_name = col_character(),
##   county_fips = col_character(),
##   county_name = col_character(),
##   lat = col_double(),
##   lng = col_double(),
##   population = col_double(),
##   density = col_double(),
##   source = col_character(),
##   military = col_logical(),
##   incorporated = col_logical(),
##   timezone = col_character(),
##   ranking = col_double(),
##   zips = col_character(),
##   id = col_double()
## )
goletasf <- uscities %>%
  st_as_sf(coords = c("lng", "lat"), crs = 4326) %>% 
  filter(city == "Goleta") %>% 
  st_transform(5070) %>% 
  st_buffer(5000) %>%
  st_bbox() %>% 
  st_as_sfc() %>% 
  st_as_sf()

elevation <- get_elev_raster(goletasf, z = 11)
## Mosaicing & Projecting
## Note: Elevation units are in meters.
goleta_elev <- crop(elevation, goletasf) 

plot(goleta_elev)

writeRaster(goleta_elev, filename = "goleta_elev.tif", overwrite = TRUE)
## Daily Exercise 18
r = raster("goleta_elev.tif")

threshold = function(x){ifelse(x <= 0, NA,1)}

m = calc(r, threshold)

ocean_cut = m * r 
plot(ocean_cut, col = viridis::viridis(256))

rcl = data.frame(min = seq(0,500,100), max = seq(100,600,100), lab = c(0:5))
rc = reclassify(ocean_cut, rcl, lowerTRUE = TRUE)

s = stack(r, m, ocean_cut, rc) %>% 
  setNames(c("elevation", "land-mask", "terrain", "topography"))

plot(s, col = viridis::viridis(256))

## Daily Exercise 19
library(osmdata)
## Data (c) OpenStreetMap contributors, ODbL 1.0. https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright
library(dplyr)
library(sf)

bb <- goletasf %>% 
  st_transform(4326) %>% 
  st_bbox() 

osm <- osmdata::opq(bb) %>% 
  add_osm_feature(key = 'amenity', value = "restaurant") %>% 
  osmdata::osmdata_sf()

print(osm)
## Object of class 'osmdata' with:
##                  $bbox : 34.3815686898973,-119.92636778984,34.4904145027731,-119.792887681268
##         $overpass_call : The call submitted to the overpass API
##                  $meta : metadata including timestamp and version numbers
##            $osm_points : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 184 points
##             $osm_lines : NULL
##          $osm_polygons : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 26 polygons
##        $osm_multilines : NULL
##     $osm_multipolygons : 'sf' Simple Features Collection with 1 multipolygons
restaurant <- osm$osm_points %>% 
  dplyr::select(osm_id, name, amenity) %>% 
  filter(!is.na(name)) %>%
  st_transform(4326)

elevation <- get_elev_raster(restaurant, z = 11)
## Mosaicing & Projecting
## Note: Elevation units are in meters.
restaurant_elev <- extract(elevation, restaurant) 

osm_rest <- restaurant %>% 
  mutate(rest_elev = restaurant_elev)

restleaflet <- leaflet(osm_rest) %>% 
  addTiles() %>% 
  addMarkers(label = osm_rest$name, popup = as.character(osm_rest$rest_elev))
restleaflet
